# StockMaster API Documentation

## Auth APIs
- **POST** /auth/signup
- **POST** /auth/login
- **POST** /auth/reset-otp
- **POST** /auth/reset
- **POST** /auth/refresh
- **POST** /auth/logout
- **GET** /auth/me

## Product APIs
- **GET** /products
- **POST** /products
- **GET** /products/:id
- **PUT** /products/:id
- **DELETE** /products/:id
- **GET** /products/:id/stock

## Warehouse APIs
- **GET** /warehouses
- **POST** /warehouses
- **GET** /warehouses/:id
- **PUT** /warehouses/:id
- **DELETE** /warehouses/:id

## Location APIs
- **GET** /locations
- **POST** /locations
- **GET** /locations/:id
- **PUT** /locations/:id
- **DELETE** /locations/:id

## Transaction APIs
- **POST** /transactions/in
- **POST** /transactions/out
- **POST** /transactions/transfer
- **POST** /transactions/adjust
- **GET** /transactions
- **GET** /transactions/:id
- **POST** /transactions/:id/status
- **GET** /transactions/history

## Dashboard APIs
- **GET** /dashboard/kpi

## User APIs (Optional)
- **GET** /users
- **GET** /users/:id
- **PUT** /users/:id

## Settings APIs (Optional)
- **GET** /settings/reorder-rules
- **POST** /settings/reorder-rules
